---
title: Chermoula Beef & Garlic Rice Bowl with Dukkah-Roasted Cauliflower & Mint Salsa
description: What do you get when you top our famous garlic rice with tender spiced beef and aromatic roasted veggies? You get a taste of the latest creation in the world of flavourful bowls! A light yoghurt and flaked almonds are the finishing touches in this bountiful meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e1faf4dacca2a007a3be5d0-ec073fed.jpg
